author: Madison Johnson
title: Madison Johnson
text: I found the prom dress of my dreams thanks to the awesome staff! The only thing is that it was very busy, but I was there on a weekend. Other than that, my experience was great like always. This was my third time there and it met my expectations from previous visits:))
